    "screen.immortality.manual.tips_intro_title": "How to Link Paths",
    "screen.immortality.manual.tips_intro_text": "On the study table, the chain must run from the starting aspect to the ending aspect through valid links. Each next aspect must connect to the previous one. If a link does not exist, the path breaks and the research will fail.",
