    "screen.immortality.manual.tips_routes_text": "Check the start and finish of the research first. Then choose intermediate aspects so every step acts as a bridge: water often leads into wood or yin, fire into yang or metal, soul into yin, spirit, or void. If a cell demands resonance, polarity, or an adjacent aspect, satisfy that condition before extending the route.",
